{"type":null,"faqId":19366,"title":"连接 WLAN 成功后经常自动断开","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-family:Frutiger Next Com;}\n.s3{font-weight:bold;}\n.s4{font-family:Frutiger Next Com;font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.22222222in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span>连接 </span><span class=\"s2\">WLAN</span><span> 成功后，请保持在 </span><span class=\"s2\">WLAN</span><span> 热点的有效距离内，避免由于距离太远导致网络信号弱从而自动断开。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>若在有效距离内仍然会出现自动断开的情况，请重启 </span><span class=\"s2\">WLAN</span><span> 开关或重启路由器。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>在 </span><span class=\"s2\">WLAN</span><span> 设置界面，点击 </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=64263\" style=\"width:0.23055555in;height:0.16319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>&gt;</span><span class=\"s3\">高级</span><span>，然后点击</span><span class=\"s3\">在休眠状态下保持 </span><span class=\"s4\">WLAN</span><span class=\"s3\"> 网络连接</span><span>，打开选项菜单，选择</span><span class=\"s3\">始终</span><span>。手机将始终保持与 </span><span class=\"s2\">WLAN</span><span> 网络的连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-1<a name=\"_Toc408418089\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=64264\" style=\"width:5.0in;height:2.5in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2507","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422608224000,"seriesProductName":"G628-TL00","visitedTimes":31,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":15,"times":5,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}